<template>

   <v-breadcrumbs id="bread" :items="breadcrumbsItemData">
     <template v-slot:item="{ item }">
       <v-breadcrumbs-item
            :to="item.to"
           :disabled="item.disabled"
       >
         {{ item.text.toUpperCase() }}
       </v-breadcrumbs-item>
     </template>
   </v-breadcrumbs>
</template>

<script>
export default {
name: "Breadcrumbs",
  data: () => ({

  }),
  props:{
    breadcrumbsItemData:{
      type:Array,
      default(){
        return{
          items: [
            {
              text: 'Dashboard',
              disabled: false,
              to: '/Dashboarda',
            },

          ],
        }

        }
      }
    }

}

</script>

<style scoped>
#bread{
  height: 5px;
  width: 100%;
}
</style>
